<div class="wrapper">
  <%= render :partial => "slider", :locals => {:btitle => @btitle, :stitle => @stitle, :search_text => @search_text} %>

  <div id="theword" class="container content-sm">
      <div class="text-center margin-bottom-50">
          <h2 class="title-v2 title-center">再見手札的特色</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="row content-boxes-v4">
          <div class="col-md-4 md-margin-bottom-40">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>完整溝通</h2>
                  <p>器捐意願、安寧意願、醫療訣擇、喪葬意願，再見手札讓您完整且方便的與家人溝通意願</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 md-margin-bottom-40">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-flash"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>快速分享</h2>
                  <p>再見手札可以快速分享您的意願給家人，輕鬆溝通這些嚴肅的議題，也希望您能分享給親朋好友，邀請大家一起加入器官捐贈的行列!</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
              <i class="pull-left fa fa-compress"></i>
              <div class="content-boxes-in-v4">
                  <h2>方便查詢</h2>
                  <p>不同於健保卡註記，再見手札讓家人隨⼿就能查詢您的意願</p>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
<legend></legend>
<div class="container content-md">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="title-v2">什麼是器官捐贈?</h2>
            <p>器官捐贈是當一個人的⽣命結束時，將可用的器官捐贈出來，移植給有需要的病⼈以延續他人生命，或使其獲得更好的⽣活品質。</p>
            <p>在台灣，捐贈者家屬若需要器官移植時將有優先權，因此器捐可以照顧您的家⼈</p><br>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 content-boxes-v3">
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">給家人永遠的照顧</h2>
                    <p>捐贈者三親等內家屬等候器官移植時將有優先權</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">幫助他人獲得重⽣</h2>
                    <p>如果您捐出5個器官,可以幫助5個家庭 ，大約可以改變20個人的人生</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">減少家⼈的經濟負擔</h2>
                    <p>捐贈者家屬最高可獲得超過35萬元 喪葬和醫療費⽤用補助</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<legend></legend>
<div class="container content-md">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="title-v2">什麼是安寧療護?</h2>
            <p>安寧療護，是指經醫師判定，罹患無法治癒之疾病，且病程近期內進展至死亡已不可避免之末期病人，臨終時得選擇不接受心肺復甦術(CPR)、不施行維生醫療、接受安寧緩和醫療。</p>
            <p>在台灣，超過三成民眾在臨終前被送到醫院接受按壓、急救、插管等「死亡套餐」酷刑，他們無謂的延長死亡過程。</p><br>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 content-boxes-v3">
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">避免無效醫療，減少末期痛苦</h2>
                    <p>臨終前使用加護病房的人中，有52.9%的人遭遇無效醫療的折磨無法善終</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">減少家屬的愧疚與自責</h2>
                    <p>要家人為自己下一個生與死的決定是困難的，易使家屬感到愧疚和自責，並引起家屬間的紛爭</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                <i class="icon-custom icon-md rounded-x icon-bg-u fa fa-lightbulb-o"></i>
                <div class="content-boxes-in-v3">
                    <h2 class="heading-sm">讓家人享有充足的醫療資源</h2>
                    <p>無效醫療病人的費用佔所有加護病房的80%，每年無效醫療付出1,700億</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
<legend></legend>
  <div id="theword" class="row fill-all-form">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-12 byenote-title">
      <h2 class="">再見手札</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-xs-12 form-page tag-box-v2 byenote-form-page">

      <%= form_for(@byenote) do |f| %>
        <%= render :partial => "organ_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>
        <%= render :partial => "hospice_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>
        <%= render :partial => "funeral_form", :locals => {:f => f} %>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="heading"><h3 style="text-align:center;"><legend>給親友的話</legend></h3></div>
          <%= f.text_area :some_message, rows: 4, :class => "message_textarea", :placeholder => "告訴親友你寫下器官捐贈、安寧及喪葬意願的原因 (注意: 此項目開放不特定人查詢及閱覽，請避免個人隱私資訊)" %>
        <div class="margin-bottom-20"></div>
          <p>*為便於查詢，以上資料開放任何人查詢及閱覽，請避免個人隱私資訊</p>
          <%= f.submit "儲存我的再見手札",:style => "width:100%;padding:10px;", :class => "btn btn-u" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= render :partial => "contactus", :locals => { } %>
</div>


